        "subject": "LU-000 lprocfs: remove useless init functions",
        "message": "LU-000 lprocfs: remove useless init functions\n\nRemove useless lprocfs initialization wrappers from all modules,\nand instead just call the initialization functions directly.\nThese wrappers have been around since the beginning of lprocfs,\nbut serve no purpose except to obfuscate the code.\n\nSigned-off-by: Andreas Dilger <adilger@whamcloud.com>\nChange-Id: I25011946208be7ee23e835f64b7a942c16c3cab0\n"
